SubString.CExoString: A portal glows softly before you. You wonder where it leads.
A portal glows softly before you. You wonder where it leads.

This stone will show you what items you will lose when going through a "wake up" portal. All items marked as ATS items will be destroyed, which inludes Containers (bags). If you have an ATS container, this container will be destroyed. EVERYTHING inside an ATS container will be destroyed too.
Using this stone, you will get messages as to what items are going to be destroyed to get a final chance to "rearrange" your inventory, so no important items are lost.
Please keep your world clean. Place your unwanted items into this barrel.
The unblinking eyes of this stature blankly return your gaze. There is no marker identifying who this figure might have been.
A portal glows softly before you. You wonder where it leads.
